<h1>Black &amp; White Macaron</h1>
<p>If you feel like antique, experimented tastes are the way to go, then this macaron is perfect for you! A solid touch of dark chocolate, enveloped by a softening touch of vanilla, will take the best of both familiar world, to carry you to a brand new experience! Because you know <em>Les Bonnes Choses</em> always finds out just how to renew your classics for you...</p>
